#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Duration Format Note"
msgstr "时长 格式 备注"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To write duration values, use the standard `java.time.Duration` format.\n"
"See the link:https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/time/Duration.html#parse(java.lang.CharSequence)[Duration#parse() javadoc] for more information."
msgstr "要写入持续时间值，请使用标准的 `java.time.Duration` 格式。更多信息请参阅 link:https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/time/Duration.html#parse(java.lang.CharSequence)[Duration#parse()] 的 link:https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/time/Duration.html#parse(java.lang.CharSequence)[Javadoc] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also use a simplified format, starting with a number:"
msgstr "您也可以使用以数字开头的简化格式："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the value is only a number, it represents time in seconds."
msgstr "如果该值仅为一个数字，则表示以秒为单位的时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the value is a number followed by `ms`, it represents time in milliseconds."
msgstr "如果该值是一个数字后跟 `“ms` ”，则表示以毫秒为单位的时间。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In other cases, the simplified format is translated to the `java.time.Duration` format for parsing:"
msgstr "在其他情况下，简化格式会被转换为 `java.time.Duration` 格式以便进行解析："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the value is a number followed by `h`, `m`, or `s`, it is prefixed with `PT`."
msgstr "如果该值是一个数字，后面跟着 `h` 、 `m` 或 `s` ，则其前面会加上 `PT` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/duration-format-note.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "If the value is a number followed by `d`, it is prefixed with `P`."
msgstr "如果该值是一个数字后跟 `字母 d` ，则会在其前面加上 `字母 P` 。"
